        "description": {
            "name": "description",
            "type": "java.lang.String",
            "value": "Due to changes introduced in 1.12, the session identifiers used under Zend Server's \"cluster\" session save handler are no longer valid (they contain a \"-\", which is specifically stripped out by _checkId()). \r\n\r\nThe actual identifier is a subsection of the identifier in this particular scenario, as one segment identifies the server on which it was originally registered."
